<Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PARAGON_DWELLING09</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Tyrea Capitol</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Kapitol Tyrea</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Names of rulers</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PARAGON_DWELLING10</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Meridan Capitol</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Kapitol Meridan</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Names of rulers</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PARAGON_DWELLING11</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Alexander Capitol</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Kapitol Aleksander</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Names of rulers</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GOVERNANCE_1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">Imperial Mandate</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Mandat imperialny</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GOVERNANCE_1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">You have the support of the Paragon to restore the empire. All who oppose you must be crushed.[br/][br/]While this is active, you no longer suffer [popularsupport6/] popular support penalties for being in a war without [casusBelli/] Casus Belli. [br/]You also recieve {influenceBonus} income per turn.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Masz poparcie Wcielenia, jeśli chodzi o odbudowę imperium. Wszyscy, którzy ci się przeciwstawią, zostaną zmiażdżeni.[br/][br/]Gdy mandat jest aktywny, nie otrzymujesz kar [anger/] do poparcia populacji za toczenie wojny bez [casusBelli/] casus belli. [br/]Zyskujesz też premię do przyrostu {influenceBonus} na turę.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">You' refers to the player who can either be male or female.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GOVERNANCE_1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PROPERTY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">Arc Affinity</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Powinowactwo do elektryczności</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GOVERNANCE_1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PROPERTY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">This unit has an affinity with Arc weaponry. All attacks with Arc weapons do {Damage} more damage and the unit gains {Resistance} Arc resistance.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ta jednostka ma powinowactwo do broni elektrycznej. Wszystkie ataki bronią elektryczną zadają {Damage} więcej obrażeń i jednostka uzyskuje {Resistance} odporność na elektryczność.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GOVERNANCE_1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EFFECT_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="s62"><Data ss:Type="String">{Damage} Arc damage</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{Damage} pkt. obrażeń elektrycznych.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PARAGON_SPAWNER_SPECIAL01</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Tarellian's Pride Base</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Duma Tarelliana</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PARAGON_SPAWNER_SPECIAL02</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Union Shield Base</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Tarcza Związku</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PARAGON_S